  "executiveSummary": {
    "problem": "Current Chronicle shipments page uses a traditional table-based UI that buries AI intelligence in columns. The narrative, blockers, and actionable insights are hidden in truncated text, making the AI investment invisible to users.",
    "solution": "Transform from data table to AI Operations Center using an exception-based management approach. Put intelligence front-and-center with a priority queue layout that surfaces problems first, shows narratives prominently, and makes actions immediately clickable.",
    "keyPrinciple": "Show me what's bleeding first (Flexport insight) - users only care about exceptions, not the 90% that's on track."
  },

